high_descs: Turn right and walk to the coffee machine.
Pick up the mug on the coffee machine.
Walk to the refrigerator on the left.
Cool the mug in the refrigerator for a few seconds, then take it out and close the refrigerator.
Turn right and walk back to the coffee machine.
Put the mug on the coffee machine, in its original position.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled mug on a coffee machine.

high_descs: turn around, walk to the coffee machine on the left
grab the cup in the coffee machine
walk to the left a little
open the refrigerator, put the cup in, wait for a while, take the cup out
walk to the right a little
put the cup in the coffee machine
anns.task_desc: cool the cup in the refrigerator, put it in the coffee machine

high_descs: Turn right to find the coffee maker on the counter to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the cup from the coffee maker.
Take a step to the left to face the fridge.
Let the cup cool in the fridge and take it back out.
Take a step to the right to face the coffee maker.
Place the cup back on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Cool down the cup on the coffee maker.
